        <p><a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">Gnoll</a> characters possess the following racial traits.</p>
        <div class="itemizedlist">
          <ul type="bullet">
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Strength +4, Constitution +2, Intelligence -2, Charisma -2.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Size <a href="ch22.html#CombatII28">Medium</a>.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p>-A <a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">gnoll's</a> base land speed is 30 feet.</p>
        <div class="itemizedlist">
          <ul type="bullet">
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Darkvision out to 60 feet.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Racial <a href="ch21s02.html#CombatI13">Hit Dice</a>: A <a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">gnoll</a> begins with two levels of <a href="ch04.html#TypesSubtypesAbilities36">humanoid</a>, which provide 2d8 <a href="ch21s02.html#CombatI13">Hit Dice</a>, a base <a href="ch21s02.html#CombatI6">attack bonus</a> of +1, and base saving throw bonuses of Fort +3, Ref +0, and Will +0.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Racial Skills: A <a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">gnoll's</a> <a href="ch04.html#TypesSubtypesAbilities36">humanoid</a> levels give it skill points equal to 5 x?(2 + Int modifier). Its class skills are <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills204">Listen</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a>.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Racial Feats: A <a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">gnoll's</a> <a href="ch04.html#TypesSubtypesAbilities36">humanoid</a> levels give it one feat.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>+1 natural armor bonus.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Automatic Languages: <a href="ch66s09.html#MonstersG125">Gnoll</a>. Bonus Languages: Common, Draconic, Elven, <a href="ch66s11.html#MonstersG136">Goblin</a>, <a href="ch70s04.html#MonstersO-R48">Orc</a>.</p>
            </li>
